        <type>void</type>
        <definition>void Dali::Ui::UiColorManager::RegisterBinding</definition>
        <argsstring>(BaseHandle view, StringView bindingId, ColorCallback callback)</argsstring>
        <name>RegisterBinding</name>
        <qualifiedname>Dali::Ui::UiColorManager::RegisterBinding</qualifiedname>
        <param>
          <type>BaseHandle</type>
          <declname>view</declname>
        </param>
        <param>
          <type>StringView</type>
          <declname>bindingId</declname>
        </param>
        <param>
          <type><ref refid="namespaceDali_1_1Ui_1a40461fcb1777fa54b9898206f3413325" kindref="member">ColorCallback</ref></type>
          <declname>callback</declname>
        </param>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Registers a named color binding for an object. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Associates <emphasis>callback</emphasis> with the given <emphasis>bindingId</emphasis>. The callback is invoked whenever the theme changes and a color has been set via UpdateBinding(). If a binding with the same <emphasis>bindingId</emphasis> already exists, it is replaced. Does not invoke the callback immediately.</para>
<para>Ownership of <emphasis>callback</emphasis> is transferred to the manager.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="in">view</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The target object </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="in">bindingId</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>A caller-defined identifier for this binding (e.g. &quot;BackgroundColor&quot;) </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="in">callback</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>A ColorCallback created via ColorCallback::New(), invoked on color table change to apply the resolved color</para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal">manager.RegisterBinding(Self(),<sp/></highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;BackgroundColor&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">,<sp/>ColorCallback::New(</highlight><highlight class="keyword">this</highlight><highlight class="normal">,<sp/>&amp;MyImpl::SetBg));</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting> </para>
        </detaileddescription>
