    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1UiColorManager" kindref="compound">UiColorManager</ref> is a Handle-based singleton that exposes color table operations (query, update) to application developers. The underlying color table and <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1View" kindref="compound">View</ref> binding management is handled internally.</para>
